supermon-ng (4.2.1-3) unstable; urgency=medium

  * postinst: generate allmon.ini on fresh install; apply NODE_STATUS_INTERVAL
    from .env via systemd drop-in; set app ownership and user_files permissions.
  * conffiles: protect user_files/favini.inc on upgrade.
  * build-deb: rebuild frontend by default (DEB_SKIP_FRONTEND_BUILD=1 to skip).
  * user_files/sbin/node_info.ini ships with mode 644.

